27 ADMINISTRATIVE AND FINANCIAL SERVICES, DEPARTMENT OF
28 Departments and Agencies - Statewide 0016
29 Initiative: Provides funding for the expansion of the requirements in current law for
30 coverage of contraceptives to include nonprescription oral hormonal contraceptives and
31 nonprescription emergency contraceptives approved by the federal Food and Drug
32 Administration. The expanded requirements apply to health plans issued or renewed on or
33 after January 1, 2026.
